Class ExpressionGraphGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.ExpressionGraphGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sf.jsqlparser.expression.ExpressionVisitor, net.sf.jsqlparser.expression.operators.relational.ItemsListVisitor

    public class ExpressionGraphGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.sf.jsqlparser.expression.ExpressionVisitor, net.sf.jsqlparser.expression.operators.relational.ItemsListVisitor
    Creates a sub-graph for visited expression. Last (root) vertex is stored in rootVertex. Data type of the visited expression is stored in dataType.
